---
import { ACQUISITION_MAILTO, SITE } from '../config/site';
---

<footer class="bg-white border-t border-slate-100">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-12 sm:py-16">
    <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl sm:rounded-3xl border border-amber-brand/25 bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-900 via-slate-950 to-amber-brand/10 p-6 sm:p-8 lg:p-12 mb-10 sm:mb-12">
      <div
        class="absolute -top-24 -right-24 w-64 h-64 rounded-full bg-amber-brand/10 blur-3xl pointer-events-none"
        aria-hidden="true"
      ></div>
      <div
        class="absolute -bottom-24 -left-24 w-64 h-64 rounded-full bg-amber-dark/10 blur-3xl pointer-events-none"
        aria-hidden="true"
      ></div>

      <div class="relative z-10 grid lg:grid-cols-[1.2fr_0.8fr] gap-10 items-center">
        <div>
          <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[3px] text-amber-400 font-extrabold mb-4">
            Domain Available for Acquisition
          </p>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl tracking-tight text-white mb-4">
            sdlreo.com — A Category-Defining Digital Asset
          </h2>
          <p class="text-slate-400 max-w-xl leading-relaxed">
            Positioned at the intersection of Scottsdale real estate branding, REO specialization,
            and premium local authority, this domain is a rare strategic asset. Serious buyers may
            inquire for pricing, transfer logistics, and escrow options.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div
          class="rounded-2xl p-6 sm:p-8 border border-white/10 bg-slate-950/90 backdrop-blur-xl"
        >
          <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[2px] text-slate-500 font-semibold mb-2">
            Acquisition Contact
          </p>
          <a
            href={`mailto:${SITE.email}`}
            class="block text-xl sm:text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-display text-white hover:text-amber-400 transition-colors break-all"
          >
            {SITE.email}
          </a>
          <a
            href={ACQUISITION_MAILTO}
            class="mt-6 inline-flex w-full items-center justify-center gap-x-3 px-6 py-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-brand to-amber-dark text-white font-extrabold rounded-2xl hover:brightness-110 transition-all"
          >
            <span>Inquire About Acquisition</span>
            <span aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span>
          </a>
          <p class="mt-4 text-[11px] text-slate-500 text-center tracking-wide">
            Confidential inquiries &bull; Response within 24 hours
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 leading-relaxed max-w-4xl mb-10">
      This website is for demonstration and informational purposes only. It does not constitute an
      offer of services, a commitment to deploy, or a guarantee of outcomes. All statistics,
      projections, and references to specific technologies are based on publicly available
      information as of July 7, 2026 and are subject to change.
    </p>

    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto py-8 text-center border-t border-slate-100">
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Part of the SDL family of premium Scottsdale &amp; Phoenix-focused domains</p>
      <div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-x-5 gap-y-2 text-sm">
        <a href="https://sdl.contact" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="font-medium text-amber-brand hover:text-amber-dark">sdl.contact</a>
        <a href="https://sdl.hair" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="font-medium text-amber-brand hover:text-amber-dark">sdl.hair</a>
        <a href="https://phx.beauty" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="font-medium text-amber-brand hover:text-amber-dark">phx.beauty</a>
        <a href="https://sdldwntwn.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="font-medium text-amber-brand hover:text-amber-dark">sdldwntwn.com</a>
        <a href="https://sdl.life" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="font-medium text-amber-brand hover:text-amber-dark">sdl.life</a>
        <a href="https://sdlrealtor.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="font-medium text-amber-brand hover:text-amber-dark">sdlrealtor.com</a>
        <a href="https://sdl.rentals" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="font-medium text-amber-brand hover:text-amber-dark">sdl.rentals</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="pt-8 border-t border-slate-100 text-xs text-slate-400 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between gap-y-3 items-center">
      <div>&copy; 2026 SDL Domains. All rights reserved. Scottsdale, Arizona.</div>
      <div>Premium real estate domains &bull; Serious buyers only</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
